<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>, uns <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fürbracht
                        etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>b<ex>ur</ex>ge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kawflewt, wie man czü Ofen etwas
                        newung gen in anczevahe maine. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, wo die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr gnad darynne anrüffen, daz ir in
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>ur</ex>ch</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willige<ex>n</ex></expan> dinst <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sein wollet, daz man sie mit sölichen <expan>newunge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>unbesw<ex>er</ex>t</expan> und <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lazz,
                        als es vormals her <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ist; und wöllet ew die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in den und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> bevolhen sein lassen. Als etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>.
                    </ab>
